  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Installation de Libelf</title>

      <para>Libelf fait partit du paquet elfutils-&elfutils-version;. Utilisez
elfutils-&elfutils-version;.tar.bz2 comme archive des sources.</para>

    <para>Préparez Libelf pour la compilation&nbsp;:</para>

    <screen><userinput remap="configure">./configure --prefix=/usr                \
            --disable-debuginfod         \
            --enable-libdebuginfod=dummy \
            --libdir=/lib</userinput></screen>

    <para>Compilez le paquet&nbsp;:</para>

<screen><userinput remap="make">make</userinput></screen>

    <para>Pour tester les résultats, lancez&nbsp;:</para>
    
<!--    <para>
One test, run-elfclassify.sh, is known to fail.</para>-->
<screen><userinput remap="test">make check</userinput></screen>



    <para>Installez seulement Libelf&nbsp;:</para>

<screen><userinput remap="install">make -C libelf install
install -vm644 config/libelf.pc /usr/lib/pkgconfig
rm /lib/libelf.a</userinput></screen>

  </sect2>

